"A possibly wooden container-type object with a natural wood color and rectangular shape. The tapered rim suggests it might be a storage box or drawer. Its structure appears to have a simple, flat design with no visible handles or latches. It seems designed for storing small items. Found on the floor near a bed in a bedroom setting, with minimal surrounding objects."

"A glossy black electronic device with a rectangular shape. The presence of cables and ports indicates it is likely a gaming console or media player. Its sleek design includes various buttons and slots. Functions as an entertainment hub. Positioned on a shelf alongside other electronics and accessories in a living room environment."

"Inconclusive evidence for the category of the object within the green bounding box. Appears to be a metallic tool-type object with a matte silver finish and angular grooves. Ambiguous function between wrench or specialized clamp. Seen in workshop environment near assembly parts."
